nh n\'b5y \'ae\'d3 b\'e6 sung, ho\'c6c thay th\'d5 c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'d5 hi\'d6n h\'b5nh. C\'b8c nh\'b5 ch\'f8c tr\'b8ch c\'e3 th\'c8m quy\'d2n c\'f1a hai N\'ad\'edc k\'fd k\'d5t s\'cf th\'abng b\'b8o cho nhau bi\'d5t nh\'f7ng thay \'ae\'e6i quan tr\'e4
ng trong c\'b8c lu\'cbt thu\'d5 c\'f1a t\'f5ng N\'ad\'edc.
\par }\pard\plain \s29\qc\sb480\sa120\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \b\f150\fs22\lang2057\cgrid {\f16 \'a7i\'d2u 3\line C\'b8C \'a7\'deNH NGH\'dcA CHUNG
\par }\pard\plain \s28\qj\fi567\sb120\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \f149\lang2057\cgrid {\f16 1. Theo n\'e9i dung c\'f1a Hi\'d6p \'ae\'denh n\'b5y, tr\'f5 tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep ng\'f7 c\'b6nh \'ae\'dfi h\'e1i c\'e3 s\'f9 gi\'b6i th\'ddch kh\'b8c:
